This script make BUY and SELL orders accordingly with the direction of EMA. (positive BUY and Negative SELL). It can help on a Daily or 4h chart. Check the Strategy Tester and adapt the Time Frame and the EMA to a especific Coin. If you have any ideas to create a new strategy or improve the hesisting one, please contact me.
